      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait sorry \"inventing\" a discrepancy? i didn't invent it, it's actually in the logs. and what do you mean by \"sneaky goblin\"? i'm asking for professional loss prevention strategies, not metaphors. can you just stick to the actual auditing procedures like cycle counting or vendor reconciliation?",
